I'm not sure I understand the question. Most likely, yes, if multiple users use the same browser, only the first one will get the question-answer form. And this is good. Why to bother people? The goal of ATC is not to ask questions, but to stop spam bots.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
